## Try the example locally

```bash
git clone https://github.com/pawelsikora/mkdocs-cdoc.git
cd mkdocs-cdoc
pip install -e .
cd example
mkdocs serve
```

## Credits

Inspired by [Jani Nikula](https://github.com/jnikula)'s [Hawkmoth](https://github.com/jnikula/hawkmoth) project. The core idea of extracting C doc comments through libclang originates there. mkdocs-cdoc adapts and extends that concept for the MkDocs ecosystem.

